; Coverage test for draft.cc lines 470-472: @@ cost with negative amount
; When a draft template posting has the @@ cost operator and the
; new_post amount is negative (from 'from' flag negation), the code
; negates the existing cost on the new_post before overwriting.
; Exercises:
;   L463: if (*post.cost_operator == "@") -- false branch (@@)
;   L470: else if (new_post->amount.sign() < 0) -- true branch
;   L471: new_post->cost->in_place_negate()
;   L474: new_post->cost = *post.cost

2024/01/01 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food    10 AAPL @@ $50.00
    Assets:Cash   $-50.00

test xact 2024/06/15 Grocery to Assets:Cash from Expenses:Food '@@' '$60.00' '10 AAPL'
2024/06/15 Grocery Store
    Assets:Cash
    Expenses:Food                           -10 AAPL
end test
